          "message": "In `getTeamsWithFallbackRoles`, the filter `AND (${orgId}::bigint IS NULL OR t.\"id\" = ${orgId} OR t.\"parentId\" = ${orgId})` uses `t.\"parentId\" = ${orgId}` which may incorrectly include teams whose parent is the org, but the intended scope is to filter teams within the organization. This could cause fallback role resolution to include teams outside the intended org hierarchy.",
          "suggestion": "Clarify the intended semantics: if the goal is to restrict to teams that are direct children of the org, the current filter is correct; if the goal is to include all descendant teams, a recursive CTE or different join condition is needed. Update the filter accordingly.",
